Open the wpa-supplicant configuration file in nano:

sudo nano /etc/wpa_supplicant/wpa_supplicant.conf

Go to the bottom of the file and add the following:

network={
    ssid="testing"
    psk="testingPassword"
}
wpa_cli -i wlan0 reconfigure


